The reason why the super personality YouTuber became a regular employee.
I asked the president who hired me (bizSPA!).
9/27 (Fri) 8:47
YouTuber is now very popular with young people.
It is not uncommon for companies to use their products for advertising, but there are companies that have started a rare mechanism called "YouTuber Adoption" that employs them as regular employees.
The company's direct marketing mix (DmMiX) is the main business of corporate CRM.
What does it mean to adopt YouTuber?
I listened to Mr. Yuki Kobayashi, Representative Director of DmMiX and Representative Director of Staff First, a subsidiary adopted by YouTuber.
I want to support young people who work hard with YouTuber.
What kind of mechanism does YouTuber adopt in the first place?
Yuki Kobayashi: The occupation of YouTuber is now a longing for many young people.
There are also top rankings in the vocational rankings that elementary school students want to get in the future, and there will be more and more young people aiming for in the future.
Until now, we have adopted and supported young people chasing dreams of bandmen and comedians.
In the same way, it is "YouTuber Adoption" to recruit young people chasing their dreams of becoming YouTuber.
Why did you decide to adopt YouTuber?
Kobayashi: While many young people are longing for the job of YouTuber, most YouTuber is not able to generate revenue as expected.
There are many creators who make and post videos while working part-time jobs, and many creators who do not allow their family to be YouTuber.
In this effort, we will provide an environment for salary and content creation to the creators we hired.
At first, we will support the demerit of YouTuber, a profession that will inevitably become unstable.
