Meeting with Mr. Atsuro and his family Leprosy | Shizuoka Shimbun at Es
Mr. Katsunobu Kato, Minister of Health, Labour and Welfare, announced at a press conference after the cabinet meeting on 27 October that he would meet with families of former leprosy patients on 2 October.
